    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.sin(0.06))
    v1 = (wp.sin(0.09) + (wp.exp(v1 + 0.16) - (tmp + 0.41 + v2 + 0.36)))
    v2 = (0.53 * v0)
    v1 = wp.cos(0.45)
    v0 = (wp.abs(tmp) - (wp.cos(tmp + 0.85) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.19)))
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.88 - v1 + 0.22) - (v2 + 0.51 / v0 + 0.40)) / ((v0 + 0.95 - v0 + 0.49) / (tmp + 0.40 - tmp + 0.25)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
